column16: Andrew Benintendi pops out to third baseman Manny Machado in foul territory.
Jackie Bradley Jr.   singles on a soft fly ball to center fielder Adam Jones.
Travis Shaw called out on strikes.
Mookie Betts pops out to shortstop Ryan Flaherty.
Corey Seager lines out sharply to shortstop J.   Hardy.
Chase Utley flies out to center fielder Adam Jones.   Howie Kendrick to 3rd.
